OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy at times in the west and
OL,6,Fthe north otherwise a day of bright
OL,7,Fspells and scattered showers. These
OL,8,Fshowers will be heavy at times in the
OL,9,Fsouth at first.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe night will be cloudy with
OL,12,Fscattered showers, these becoming
OL,13,Ffrequent and merging into longer
OL,14,Fperiods of rain at times. Becoming
OL,15,Fless frequent towards morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FBright or sunny spells will
OL,18,Fincrease form the morning. These will
OL,19,Fbe interspersed with the occasional
OL,20,Fshower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
