OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith rain spreading to the southwest
OL,7,FSaturday. Rain continues Sunday,
OL,8,Fbecoming heavy in the southwest. Early
OL,9,Frain turns showery before clearing to
OL,10,Fbright spells later Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
